2C%20and%20meetings%20everyday.%20One%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20chaotic%20period%20in%20my%2040-plus%20years%20that%20I've%20been%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20like%20Osario%20worry%20that%20a%20July%208%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-ruling-trump-firings-federal-agencies-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20ruling%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20additional%20staff%20cuts%20at%20the%20agency%2C%20though%20none%20have%20been%20announced.%20The%20court%20decision%20will%20allow%20the%20Trump%20administration%20to%20continue%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-workers-scotus-decision-trump-doge-firings-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereduction%20of%20the%20federal%20workforce%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20performance%20metrics%20have%20gone%20downhill%20in%20recent%20months%20based%20on%20actions%20already%20taken%2C%26quot%3B%20Jessica%20LaPointe%2C%20a%20union%20president%20who%20represents%20SSA%20workers%2C%20told%20BI%2C%20adding%20that%20cuts%20would%20reduce%20service.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20at%20historically%20low%20staffing%20levels%20compared%20to%20the%20number%20of%20beneficiaries%20we%20serve.%20We%20simply%20can't%20afford%20to%20lose%20any%20more%20workers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2293e17e49-7c9c-463e-9563-35cadf7b56cd%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPublic%20data%20is%20vanishing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20workers%20and%20beneficiaries%20raise%20alarms%20about%20understaffing%2C%20wait%20times%20are%20becoming%20more%20difficult%20to%20track.%20The%20SSA%20used%20to%20display%20metrics%20showing%20live%20data%20on%20wait%20times%2C%20callback%20times%2C%20and%20historical%20data%2C%20per%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.ph%2Foj7ms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earchived%20version%20of%20a%20webpage%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ssa.gov%2Fssa-performance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esite%20shows%20aggregated%20data%20from%20the%20fiscal%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20no%20longer%20displays%20the%20live%20wait%20times.%20Per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fpolitics%2F2025%2F06%2F20%2Fsocial-security-wait-times-cuts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20250000000000*%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.ssa.gov%2Fssa-performance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInternet%20Archive%20snapshots%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20webpages%20seem%20to%20have%20shifted%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20250608141622%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.ssa.gov%2Funder-maintenance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearly%20June%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20recently%20that%20some%20really%20key%20data%20elements%20in%20terms%20of%20wait%20times%20for%20their%20800%20service%20and%20details%20about%20the%20disability%20processing%20wait%20times%20are%20not%20readily%20available%2C%26quot%3B%20Jack%20Smalligan%2C%20a%20senior%20policy%20fellow%20at%20the%20Urban%20Center%20and%20an%20SSA%20alum%2C%20told%20BI.%20He%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20disconcerting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20SSA%20commissioner%20Martin%20O'Malley%20also%20told%20BI%20that%20he%20had%20noticed%20the%20agency%20has%20removed%20a%20slew%20of%20public-facing%20metrics%2C%20which%20he%20believes%20%26quot%3Bundermines%20credibility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20the%20thickest%20businessman%20can%20figure%20out%20that%20if%20you%20have%20an%20all-time%20high%20number%20of%20customers%20growing%2C%20growing%2C%20growing%20every%20day%2C%20every%20day%2C%20every%20day%2C%20and%20you%20reduce%20the%20staff%20to%20a%2050-year%20low%2C%20customer%20service%20is%20going%20to%20suffer%2C%26quot%3